IMAGEMASH
by pops

an image batch processor written in python and pyqt 
with some cool thing such as preview and interactive tools

it is released under the GNU GPL V3

the software is in developement
there are only 3 plugin working now:
    a crop plugin
    a resize plugin
    a flip/rotate plugin

Thunar custom action:
xterm -hold -e "python3 /media/donees/programation/imagemash/imagemash.py %F"

